replies.body:
@Juves, how do you feel about the jungle role with the potential of the assassin meta coming back slowly into the jungle? How do you keep being an ALPHA MALE with 600IQ and yet maintain the greatest hairline in OCE? 

@Dhokla, how are you liking OCE? Better than NA right? In all seriousness, how does OCE SoloQ differ from NA SoloQ aside from toxicity? It's great to see you come to OCE. Enjoy your stay here and hope you guys do well again this split and hope you don't go back to NA :( 

@Ry0ma, did you feel pressured during your first international tournament? Regardless of the result, you showed up in that tournament and it was impressive to  see someone as young as you and FBI become pro-gamers and still show up in high-pressure environments! Respect. Also, how's the midlane meta going to shape with the new brambleback item and lethality buffs?

@FBI, being at such a young age, how did your parents go about with you becoming a pro-gamer? You did really good for your first international tournament and it was awesome to watch you play like that! Keep up the great work and I hope I see your growth within the Esports industry in Australia :D

@Rogue, does anyone else call you Justin Bieber? You had a great run at RR and I hope I get to see more of your Thresh this split :D Keep up the great work! 

@Bencel, do you have a specific routine that the players have to follow? It would be awesome to know what kind of routine they follow daily. 

Thanks guys, #OPLFAMILY #SINWIN
